sirikali (1.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=low
  [Mhogo Mchungu]
  * New Features
     -- Add ability to add a favorite volume with mount options
        (external config file path,idle timeout,auto mount).
     -- Add a GUI option to select what secure key storage backend
        to use when auto mounting volumes.

